title: Independent Candidate Aqeel Malik wins NA-54 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Candidate Aqeel Malik has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-54, Rawalpindi III by securing 85,912 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent Candidate Azra Masood, who bagged 73,694 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 50.57 percent.
